I",<h3 id="in-a-nutshell">In a nutshell</h3>

<p class="nutshell">Organisations will maximise their returns if they are driven by a transcendent purpose. This book suggests five steps for achieving a business driven by ideals.</p>

<ol class="nutshell">
  <li>Identify a brand ideal that improves people’s lives through eliciting joy, enabling connection, inspiring exploration, evoking pride or impacting society.</li>
  <li>Build your organisation’s culture around these ideals</li>
  <li>Communicate the brand ideal to engage both employees and customers</li>
  <li>Deliver an excellent customer experience</li>
  <li>Regularly evaluate your progress in achieving this brand ideal</li>
</ol>

